[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "本日は、果ての大陸到達を祈願しての記念式典を\n催していただき、まことにありがとうございます",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00286",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "私も王族を代表して同乗し、いまだ見ぬ新世界、\n潤沢なるマナを蓄えし大地に向けて歩んでまいります",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00287",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "――錬金術が栄えていた時代には、たくさんの夢が\n錬金術によって実現されようとしていました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00288",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "空を泳ぐ船や、遠い地を瞬時に繋ぐ道など……\n今では考えられぬようなことが、たくさん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00289",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "マナの恵みが途絶え、錬金術が衰退した今では\n叶わぬことかもしれませんが――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00290",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "クレオ",
		"romanized_name": "Cleo",
		"model_path_hash": "1405587059148187981",
		"text": "今こそ、その未来を掴む時！\n果てへ到達し、錬金術による未来を皆で描きましょう！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_234_038_00291",
		"still_path_hash": "6779436863461642750",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "さすが我が妹、立派な演説だったね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00292",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ユナ",
		"romanized_name": "Juna",
		"model_path_hash": "7176586596496405136",
		"text": "はい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_070_038_00293",
		"still_path_hash": "6403040722015916711",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "聴衆Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "錬金術の未来か……！\n実現できたら、生活が豊かになりそうだな！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_724_038_00294",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "聴衆Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "でも、本当にマナがあるのかは分からないんだよな……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_725_038_00295",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "聴衆Ａ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "たとえなかったとしても、今までと変わらないだけだ。\nなら見つけたときのことを考えようぜ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_724_038_00296",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "聴衆Ｂ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "そうだな！　やりたいことがたくさん浮かぶよ。\n私も錬金術、使えたりしないかな……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_725_038_00297",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "皆の期待が嬉しいね、同志！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00298",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "はい、とっても！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00299",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "クレオ様が王族代表ってことは、殿下は居残り？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00300",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "リヒャルト・ランターナは居残りだね。\nでもね、冒険者ロマン・カルマンはもちろん同行するよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00301",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "だ、大丈夫なんですか？　危険な船旅になりますし、\nもし何かあったら王子と王女を一斉に失うことに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00302",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "そうだね。でもね、冒険者に同じ質問をしてごらん。\n全員が全員、大丈夫！って答えると思うよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00303",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ユナ",
		"romanized_name": "Juna",
		"model_path_hash": "7176586596496405136",
		"text": "はぁ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_070_038_00304",
		"still_path_hash": "6403040722015916711",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ユナさん……当然殿下を説得したんだろうな。\nそれで止められなかった、と……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00305",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ユナ",
		"romanized_name": "Juna",
		"model_path_hash": "7176586596496405136",
		"text": "レスナ、イザナ、そちらは任せたぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_070_038_00306",
		"still_path_hash": "6403040722015916711",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "レスナ/イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00307_2",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "はい！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00308",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "司会",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "では続きまして、フロッケ号を指揮するランツェ様",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_717_038_00309",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "ふふっ、ランツェさん、めちゃくちゃ緊張してる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00310",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "演説の原稿、何度も書き直して練習してたもんね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00311",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "ご紹介にあずかりました、ランツェ・ダッハです。私は\n船長として、この航海で必ずや果ての大陸を発見し――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00312",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "マナを持ち帰り、ランターナの皆様へ\n吉報を届けられるよう、全力で邁進していく所存……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00313",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あれ、黙っちゃった？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00314",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ロマン",
		"romanized_name": "Roman",
		"model_path_hash": "2044084852602675005",
		"text": "緊張でど忘れしちゃったかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_049_038_00315",
		"still_path_hash": "2419706081160656678",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "ふぅ……やっぱやめだ。かたっくるしいのは似合わねえ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00316",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "レスナ！　最初、俺はお前に、\n果ての大陸へ行くのはやめとけって言ったよな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00317",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "え！？\nは、はい……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00318",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "外海は恐ろしいバケモンがうようよしてる。俺は過去に\n失敗したし、暗黒の氷海でも実際一度は逃げてきた",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00319",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "でもよ、失敗や逃げは負けじゃねえ。\nその経験を活かして、最終的に上手くいきゃいいんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00320",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "レスナ、あの頃から比べてお前は立派になった。\nおかげでそばにいた俺もちったあ成長できたらしい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00321",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "ランターナのみんなの想い、俺のかつての船のみんな、\nそしてバーバラ……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00322",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "俺がこれまで関わってきた奴も、そうでない奴も\n全員の想いを一緒に持っていく！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00323",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "んで、全員果ての大陸に送り届けて、\n全員無事にここ、ランターナに送り返す！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00324",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "7966048589802988617",
		"text": "以上！　フロッケ号船長ランツェ・ダッハ！\n野郎ども錨を上げろ！　出航だ！！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_053_038_00325",
		"still_path_hash": "5608676279601578000",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "聴衆",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ランツェ！　ランツェ！　ランツェ！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_727_038_00326_00",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "7061794453237574237",
		"text": "あーあ、結局地が出ちゃった",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_038_00327",
		"still_path_hash": "7010833269667927555",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "6823802507187778884",
		"text": "あはは……でも、ランツェさんらしいよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00328",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（私は……私たちは、いよいよ果ての大陸へと\n　たどり着く）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00329",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（果たして、そこには何があるのだろう？）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00330",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（伝承通り、無尽蔵のマナがあるのかな。\n　もしかしたら、本当は何もないのかもしれない）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00331",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（いずれにせよ、１つの夢が終わりを迎え、\n　錬金術のこれからが決まるのだろう）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00332",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（それが明るいものであっても、暗いものであっても。\n　……覚悟はできてる）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00333",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（出航の、時だ）",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_038_00334",
		"still_path_hash": "2457375212832216718",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]